<dl id="n06154o"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06154o">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06154o"> 154(o)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 1<sup>st</sup> fruits of them that slept</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">ELEVENTH ARTICLE. &ldquo;THE RESURRECTION OF THE BODY.&rdquo;&ldquo;THE PROOF AND PLEDGE OF OUR RESURRECTION.&rdquo;&mdash;The resurrection of Christ from the dead is that pledge. &ldquo;Because I live ye shall live also.&rdquo; &ldquo;Now is Christ risen from the dead, and become <mark>the first-fruits of them that slept</mark>.&rdquo; <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 25-6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
